		## Managing Variables ##
		########################
Note: This work should be done in ~/dev-vars-playbook

Task 1 - Create a playbook that does following things :
	a) Installs apache webserver
	b) Opens ports for the service to be reachable
	c) It must query web server to ensure its up and running

Task 2 - Make use of following variables in playbook:
	web_pkg: httpd
	firewall_pkg: firewalld
	web_service: httpd
	firewall_service: firewalld
	python_pkg: python-httplib2
	rule: http

Task 3 - Also add a task to put "This is variables exercise" in /var/www/html/index.html

Task 4 - Spend 15 Minutes to minutes define variables in different ways as discussed during discussion.
